# Lychgate Critical Allowlist — domains that should NEVER be blocked
#
# Format:
#   exact-domain.com         — exact match
#   *.exact-domain.com       — wildcard matching any subdomain
#
# SAFETY: wildcards with fewer than 2 dots in suffix are rejected
# (e.g. *.com is refused because it would void the entire block).
#
# Entries in this list ALWAYS win over any blocklist.

# ============================================================
# Apple — system-critical, do not block
# ============================================================
# Code signature validation (blocking this slows every signed app launch)
ocsp.apple.com
ocsp2.apple.com
crl.apple.com
crl3.digicert.com
ocsp.digicert.com

# Captive portal detection (WLAN reachability)
captive.apple.com
www.apple.com

# Software updates
swcdn.apple.com
swdist.apple.com
swdownload.apple.com
mesu.apple.com
gdmf.apple.com
gg.apple.com

# App Store
itunes.apple.com
buy.itunes.apple.com
init-buy.itunes.apple.com
valid.apple.com
gsra.apple.com
gsa.apple.com
*.mzstatic.com

# Time sync
time.apple.com
time-ios.apple.com
time-macos.apple.com

# iCloud (if you use it)
gateway.icloud.com
api.apple-cloudkit.com

# ============================================================
# Common services you probably want — uncomment / edit as needed
# ============================================================

